T02TD2417E:35b-1: aa ti yo ga bh'a ba na n'a ma /
T02TD2417E:35b-3: aa ti rnal 'byor gyi sgom pa'i thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD2417E:35b-5: dur khrod brgyad la 'jigs byed brgyad //
T02TD2417E:35b-6: dus mtha'i me 'bar khams gsum bsreg / tshangs pa'i go nas du ba 'thul //
T02TD2417E:35b-8: rdo rje ze 'bru'i dbus su ni //
T02TD2417E:35b-9: nyi ma'i gdan steng gnas pa de //
T02TD2417E:35b-10: nam mkha'i 'od chen h'um nyid sgrogs //
T02TD2417E:35b-11: mdzes pa'i sems nyid rgyu ba yin //
T02TD2417E:35b-13: ri bong can gyis mdud pa bkrol //
T02TD2417E:35b-14: nyams myong dpa' bo rang rig rgyal //
T02TD2417E:35b-15: lhan cig skyes pa'i bdag / mgon po nyid ni bsam par gyis //
T02TD2417E:35b-17: de nyid dur khrod me yin ta //
T02TD2417E:35b-18: de nyid smra dang zla rgyan 'dzag / skye rga shi dang khams gsum gnas //
T02TD2417E:35b-19: rang nyid dran te de nyid mthong //
T02TD2417E:35b-20: 'di ni gnyis med dbyibs dang bral //
T02TD2417E:35b-21: dngos po'i cho 'phrul brdzun pa ste //
T02TD2417E:35b-22: sems nyid 'khrul pas ma rtogs so //
T02TD2417E:35b-23: aa ti'i rnal 'byor rig pa med //
T02TD2417E:35b-24: ji ltar bzhag pa de ltar yin //
T02TD2417E:35b-25: gnyis med sems la rtag lta dang //
T02TD2417E:35b-26: chad par 'gyur ba 'ang ma yin no //
T02TD2417E:35b-27: de phyir nyi zla'i dbus su ni //
T02TD2417E:35b-28: phra ba'i h'um nyid bsgom par gyis //
T02TD2417E:36a-0: aa ti rnal 'byor gyi bsgom po'i man ngag ces bya ba slob dpon klu'i @36a * //
T02TD2417E:36a-1: byang chub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
